### PG Simulator 콜백 테스트 - 결제 성공
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "12345",
  "transactionKey": "TXN_12345_SUCCESS",
  "status": "APPROVED",
  "message": "결제 성공",
  "amount": 10000,
  "approvalNo": "APPROVAL_12345"
}

